abstract: The circle of those who saw video of a coach’s abusive acts as soon as December was wider than had been understood.
snippet: The circle of those who saw video of a coach’s abusive acts as soon as December was wider than had been understood.
lead_paragraph: NEW BRUNSWICK, N.J. — As Rutgers officials tried Friday to calm the public furor over their handling of abusive behavior by the Scarlet Knights’ men’s basketball coach, the university president and athletic director presented conflicting depictions of who was responsible for the decision to keep the coach on staff after administrators first learned of his behavior.

abstract: Sara Schechner and Kenneth Launie bonded over a shared love of science and history.
snippet: Sara Schechner and Kenneth Launie bonded over a shared love of science and history.
lead_paragraph: When the call came in April 2004, it was hard for Kenneth Launie to contain his enthusiasm. An amateur collector and restorer of telescopes, he had seen the instrument before, but only behind the glare of a glass case at Harvard. Then, out of nowhere, came the offer: Bring your white gloves and your screwdriver, and take apart the telescope that had been used by John Winthrop, a Harvard professor and descendant of the Massachusetts Bay Colony founder, to observe the transit of Venus in 1769.

lead_paragraph: In Vatican City on Monday, the College of Cardinals will gather to decide on when to hold the papal conclave to select the next pope. There are no polls of the 115 cardinals who will vote in the conclave, and FiveThirtyEight is not making any predictions. But plenty of others are — notably, bookies and bettors.

abstract: American Greetings Corporation, Cleveland, chose Mullen, Boston, part of the Interpublic Group of Companies, as agency of record for creative duties, digital ads and media planning and buying.
snippet: American Greetings Corporation, Cleveland, chose Mullen, Boston, part of the Interpublic Group of Companies, as agency of record for creative duties, digital ads and media planning and buying.
lead_paragraph: American Greetings Corporation, Cleveland, chose Mullen, Boston, part of the Interpublic Group of Companies, as agency of record for creative duties, digital ads and media planning and buying. The account, with spending estimated at $3 million, had been handled by Element 79, Chicago, which its parent, the Omnicom Group, merged into another Omnicom agency, the Chicago office of DDB Worldwide. The media duties had been handled by an Omnicom media agency, PHD.
